{
  "chapter": 49,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述了寇仲和徐子陵在沈落雁庄园的惊险遭遇。徐子陵潜入沈落雁闺房时遭遇\"影子刺客\"杨虚彦的伏击，身受重伤。寇仲为救徐子陵，不顾暴露行藏，高呼\"有贼\"以惊动沈落雁等人。二人躲藏疗伤后，寇仲独自返回沈落雁处谈判，以假名册换取素素的自由。沈落雁虽识破诡计，但因对徐子陵之死的复杂情感，最终放走了三人。本章展现了寇仲的机智勇敢、徐子陵的深厚内功，以及沈落雁对徐子陵的微妙情感。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有贼！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢来生事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小陵！小陵！你吓死我了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是什么地方？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎能把素姐一个人留在那里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是别无选择下才这么做，放心吧！你在这里歇一会，待我去把素姐接来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不快去，素姐胆子这么小，吓都吓坏她了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以沈落雁的精明，自能从我遗在楼内的短戟知道是我们在搞事，加上见到逃走的只有我们两人，哪还猜不到素姐定在附近。所以素姐现在十成十已落到她的手上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那怎办才好！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再助我行功运气，天明时，我们就一起去找沈落雁把素姐救回来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "落雁娇妻，为夫仲少爷回来了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先把名册交出来，我们再谈其他事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若非小陵为你挡了昨夜那个家伙一剑，美人儿你早玉殉香消。现在一见面便毫不客气。唉！像你这么美的人儿俯拾即是，但像你那么无情无义的，则肯定是空前绝后哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真拿你这两个小鬼头没法，竟懂得躲到我这里来。好吧！你将名册交出来，奴家便将你的素姐送还你，又任你们出城，以后的事，只好看你们的造化了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈美人你真懂说笑，看准小陵受了伤，所以不虔我们能走多远。哈！让我告诉你真相吧！小陵根本没有事，看！他不是站在你背后吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要再装模作样了。小陵留下的大滩血迹，谁都骗不了。以影子刺客杨虚彦的身手，若被他刺中而不死的，他该可算是第一人哟！",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那家伙原来是杨虚彦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要骗我，徐子陵是否死了？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫要胡猜，名册现正在他手上，若我可和素姐安然回去，保证他立即把名册交回。否则过了时限，他会立即逃走，把名册交到杨广手上，那时你们瓦岗军立时断绝了所有的情报消息，变得又聆又盲。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小陵是否死了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要问了，你究竟是否肯把人交出来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不用骗我，小陵已死了。若我把你擒下，保证可从你身上将名册搜出来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "即管放马过来，若你能取回完整的名册，我的名字以后就倒转来叫。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的尸身在哪里？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他生前不见你关心他，死后你反爱问长问短，这是怎么一回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个不关你事。立即把名册还我，我便放你和素素离开，保证绝不追击，至于如何过得世勋城防那一关，就恩小女子无能为力。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先交书后放人。哼！莫忘了纵被你毁去名册，我们只要费点工夫，就可重新编出另一簿出来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然你不怕失去了以前所有往来的帐目，又不怕延误时间，那我索性把册子毁去，再和你们拼个生死，横竖小陵死了，我和素姐都不想活呢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！罢了！但有些事我亦难以作主。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给我把素素带出来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小陵是否死了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一手交书，一手交人，我保证手下不追击你们。只要一个不字，我立使素素尸横地上，然后全力把你杀死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放人吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "莫成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小姐不好，这小子竟敢骗我们。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看他们能逃到哪里去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道他还未死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到沈婆娘真会上当。",
      "tone": "欢喜",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的计策是厉害，首先算准沈婆娘会在那里等我们回去救人，更算准她情愿把素姐还给我们，好增加我们逃走的困难性，只不过仍算漏了一样东西。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来她很着紧你哟！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "管她娘着紧不着紧，这女人送给我都不会要。",
      "tone": "不屑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈婆娘有否对姐姐不好呢？",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她骗我说已拿下了小仲，逼我把这几天的事说出来，姐姐只好说了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "素姐没提及关于黍青楼的事吧！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然没有，姐姐岂是那么不识轻重的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你算很大命的呢！原来那伤你的家伙就是连我们老爹都敢行刺的影子刺客杨虚彦。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若非我及时运功把他攻入内的真劲化去，区区一本簿子绝救不了我的命。哼！今趟我们若能逃出生天，就要他的好看。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "得罪了我们扬州双龙的人，定没有好下场，像沈婆娘这几天便保证睡难安寝。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我恐怕亦至少有几天不能和人动手，假若佩佩帮不了我们的忙，就只好以真名册去换取自由了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 307
    }
  ],
